<br>
And like EQ, the level ranges of the colours increases as the levels go up.<br>
<br>
All equipment has a level as well. And you have to use equipment that is suitable for your level. Bascially, they wanted to make the game equipment orientated, but with no twinking, so this is how they did it. You cant equip an uber item from a high level dungeon, because it would break after the first hit.<br>
